name: Cocoa Mousse Vintage Finger Lovely
description:
This Cocoa Mousse Vintage Finger Lovely (TM) features a green and brown vintage buttons. Mounted on a silver-toned adjustable ring. Gift box included.

All rings are made from vintage/antique buttons and cabochons and are adjustable to fit just about any size!

*These rings are not intended for young children. These rings have small pieces that can be a choking hazard*
